+        <h1>Carbon Laser Facial — Pre &amp; Post-Care Guide</h1>
+        <p style="font-size:1.05rem; color:var(--color-text-light, #574C3F);">Carbon Laser (Q-Switch) Facial gives an immediate glow, but a little preparation and simple aftercare make the difference between a good result and a great one.</p>
+        <p><a href="/services/carbon-laser-facial" class="btn btn--outline">See Carbon Laser Facial details &rsaquo;</a></p>
