+        <h2>When to Call Us</h2>
+        <p>Please contact your clinic on <a href="tel:+917703037070"><strong>+91 77030 37070</strong></a> if you experience any of the following after your Chemical Peel session:</p>
+        <ul class="care-list care-list--alert">
+              <li>Severe pain, sustained burning, or hot skin beyond the first day</li>
+              <li>Blistering, open sores, or unusually dark scabbing</li>
+              <li>Signs of infection — pus, spreading redness, or fever</li>
+        </ul>
+        <p style="margin-top:1rem; color:var(--color-text-light, #574C3F);">These are precautionary — serious problems are uncommon, but early contact is always the safer choice.</p>
