+        <h1>Hair PRP — Pre &amp; Post-Care Guide</h1>
+        <p style="font-size:1.05rem; color:var(--color-text-light, #574C3F);">PRP uses growth factors from your own blood, so the better nourished and rested you are, the better your plasma quality and the better the results. Simple aftercare protects your scalp while it works.</p>
+        <p><a href="/services/hair-prp" class="btn btn--outline">See Hair PRP details &rsaquo;</a></p>
+      </div>
