+        <h1>Laser Hair Removal — Pre &amp; Post-Care Guide</h1>
+        <p style="font-size:1.05rem; color:var(--color-text-light, #574C3F);">Following these pre-care and post-care instructions makes your laser hair removal session more comfortable, more effective, and safer for your skin. Your practitioner will review these with you at your consultation and answer any questions.</p>
